<div class="wysiwyg-container">
    <div class="wysiwyg-header">
        <h3>Text Editor WYSIWYG</h3>
        <p>Select text to view and format in real time.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="wysiwyg-toolbar">
        <button class="wysiwyg-btn"  title="Negrita" onmousedown="{{texttoBold}}">
            <b>B</b>
        </button>
        <button class="wysiwyg-btn" title="Itálica" onmousedown="{{texttoItalic}}">
            <i>I</i>
        </button>
        <button class="wysiwyg-btn" title="Subrayado" onmousedown="{{texttoUnderline}}">
            <u>U</u>
        </button>
        <button class="wysiwyg-btn"  title="Tachado" onmousedown="{{texttoStrikethrough}}">
            <s>S</s>
        </button>
        <button class="wysiwyg-btn btn-highlight"  title="Resaltar" onmousedown="{{colorMarker}}">
            R
        </button>
    </div>
    
    <div class="wysiwyg-editor" contenteditable="true" >
    <b>Welcome to myVanilla.js!</b> <span style="background-color: yellow;">This is a reactive <u>WYSIWYG</u></span> text editor built entirely in <b><span style="background-color: yellow;"></span></b>vanilla <b><span style="background-color: yellow;">JavaScript</span></b> with no <s>external dependencies</s>. <u>Try selecting text and applying styles from the top toolbar.</u>    </div>
    <div class="wysiwyg-footer">
        <div class="footer-stat">
            <span>myVanila.js/wysiwyg </span>
            <span class="selection-badge">By Enocwtc@gmail.com</span>
        </div>
        
    </div>
</div>
